          <div class="back News"><div class="featured-events-back-wrapper"><h3 class="featured-event-location"></h3><h2 class="featured-event-title">Book Club in a Bag</h2><h4 class="featured-event-date"><div class="featured-event-day"></div><div class="featured-event-time"></div></h4><p class="featured-event-info">Do you belong to a book club? Would you like to start one? We'd like to help! The Book Club in a Bag program has most everything you need to get started. It comes with 8 copies of a book, a discussion guide with suggested questions and a sign-out sheet for the group leader. We have over 90 titles on hand for you to choose from. 
Just added is The Dovekeepers, by Alice Hoffman Place a hold today!
 
